text: Banshidhar Bhagat is an Indian politician and member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. Bhagat is a member of the Uttarakhand Legislative Assembly from the Kaladhungi constituency in Nainital district.Will Kaladhungi BJP legislator Bhagat be sixth time lucky?My NetaBahuguna joins former BJP chief ministers in party posters Presently he is the state president of BJP in Uttrakhand since 16 Jan 2020 == References == Category:People from Nainital district Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Uttarakhand Category:Members of the Uttarakhand Legislative Assembly Category:Living people Category:Uttarakhand MLAs 2017– Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:State Presidents of Bharatiya Janata Party
